\c 6
\s Kusarudzwa kwamadhikoni manomwe
\p
\v 1 Zvino namazuva iwayo, apo uwandu hwavadzidzi huchiwedzera, maHerenisiti akanyunyutira vaHebheru, nokuti chirikadzi dzavo dzaidarikwa pakugoverwa komusi mumwe nomumwe.
\v 2 Zvino vanegumi navaviri vakadanira kwavari chaunga chevadzidzi, vakati: Hazvina kunaka kuti isu tirege shoko raMwari, tishumire pamatafura.
\v 3 Naizvozvo hama, tarirai pakati penyu varume vanomwe vanopupurirwa zvakanaka, vazere noMweya Mutsvene nenjere, vatingagadza pabasa iri.
\v 4 Asi isu tichatsungirira pakunyengetera napabasa reshoko.
\v 5 Shoko rikafadza chaunga chose; vakasaa Stefano, murume wakanga azere nokutenda noMweya Mutsvene, naFiripi, naProkoro, Nikanori, naTimoni, naPamenasi, naNikorasi, muproserite weAndiyokiya.
\v 6 Vavakaisa pamberi pavaapositora; vakati vanyengetera vakaisa mavoko pamusoro pavo.
\v 7 Shoko raMwari rikakura, uwandu hwevadzidzi hukakura paJerusarema; navapristi vazhinji vakateerera kutenda.
\s Stefano unovurawa
\p
\v 8 Zvino Stefano azere nenyasha nesimba wakaita zvishamiso zvikuru nezviratidzo zvikuru pakati pavanhu.
\v 9 Ipapo kukamuka vamwe vesinagoge rinonzi raVasununguki, navaKureni, navaArekisandira, naveKirikia, neveAsiya, vachikakavadzana naStefano.
\v 10 Asi vakanga vasingagoni kumirisana novuchenjeri noMweya waaitaura nawo.
\v 11 Ipapo vakafurira varume pachivande, vaiti: Takamunzwa achitaura mashoko anomhura maererano naMozisi naMwari.
\v 12 Vakamutsa vanhu, navakuru navanyori, vaka\add mu\add*svikira vakamubata vakamuvuisa kudare,
\v 13 vakaisapo zvapupu zvenhema, zvaiti: Munhu uyu haatongomiri kutaura mashoko anomhura imba iyi tsvene nomurairo,
\v 14 nokuti takamunzwa achiti: Uyu Jesu weNazareta uchaparadza nzvimbo iyi uye uchashandura tsika Mozisi dzaakakumikidza kwatiri.
\v 15 Zvino vose vakanga vagere padare vakamudzvokora vakavona chiso chake sechainge chiso chomutumwa.
